Message: Hi, Iâ€™m the NewsBreak Ad Assistant. How can I help?
The user completes the submission of the form
Hi, could you help me with some things?
Of course! I'm here to help. What do you need assistance with?

I'm new to the platform and I'm thrilled with the advertising opportunities... I'm in the process of trying to learn everything on my own, as I haven't found anyone qualified or familiar with the platform, and I've found little content online...
Do you have any study material or recommend someone I can use for content?

I'm currently watching a video of you using RedTrack; it looks excellent...

Welcome to News Break! It's great to hear you're excited about the advertising opportunities. We have a Help Center with articles that cover various topics, including getting started with advertising on our platform. You can find guides on creating ad accounts, managing your account, and more. Here's a link to our Account Management Guide: [Account Management Guide](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/17539290349709-Account-Management-Guide). 

Additionally, we host monthly webinar training sessions that you might find helpful. Make sure you're subscribed to our email updates so you don't miss out on these sessions.

If you have specific questions about using RedTrack or any other tracking platform, feel free to ask, and I'll do my best to assist you!
Perfect, I'm very interested in the monthly training, where can I sign up?

To sign up for our monthly webinar training sessions, make sure you're subscribed to our email updates. We send out notifications with details on how to register for these sessions. If you're not already subscribed, you can do so through your account settings or by contacting our support team at adsupport@newsbreak.com. Let me know if you need any more help!
Thank you very much, may our partnership be prosperous!
You're welcome! I'm sure our partnership will be successful. If you have any more questions or need assistance, feel free to reach out. Have a great day!
